latestPosts.caption:
Wild. Fearless. Unstoppable. | #WomensDay2025 ✨🌿

This #InternationalWomensDay, we had the honor of hosting Ashima Batra, founder of Dorabi and Aamili, at Ramisera Wilds—a woman who embodies courage, creativity, and the spirit of entrepreneurship.

Fresh from her winning pitch on Shark Tank India Season 4, Ashima took a well-deserved break in the wilderness, where nature’s untamed beauty mirrors the journey of every trailblazing woman—bold, unpredictable, and extraordinary.

Her story is a reminder that true success isn’t just about breaking barriers but about rewriting the rules. Here’s to every woman who dares to dream, disrupt, and dominate!

#WomenWhoLead #SharkTankIndia #Entrepreneurship #RamiseraWilds #Dorabi #Aamili #FearlessWomen #IWD2025 #WildAndFree #SheMeansBusiness

latestPosts.caption: Challenge #2 I thought I was simply taking on a challenge to embrace patience ; to steady my hands, quiet my mind, and surrender to the rhythm of the wheel. But as the clay took shape, so did my understanding of creation itself. I realized that just like in building a fashion brand, true artistry lies not in forcing perfection but in allowing the process to unfold with grace. This experience was essential for me—not just as a test of patience, but as a lesson in trust. Because whether in clay or in business, the most beautiful forms emerge when we find harmony between control and flow. ✨

GRWM ft @batraashima 
The makeup, the hair and The dress that made it all happen! The fun and excitement of being on TV and that too in front of such important people, was nerve wrecking, But a girl’s gotta do what a girl’s gotta do, and for us it was to Shine ✨💖
Meet my life’s board of directors 🥂🧿
